    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Ogma, a mercenary from Talys. If you need strength put to a task...I'm your man.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "Days like this remind me of my time as a gladiator. And some things not worth remembering...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I have three men I trust completely: Bord, Cord, and Barst. All three are true warriors.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Rest when you can. You have to be ready to move whenever fighting breaks out.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Can you use a sword? I'm looking for a sparring partner. Not that I'm good at holding back...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I take care of my sword to make sure it doesn't rust. It's a habit that's served me for a long time.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You're <Player Name>? My employer sent me to say hello. Oh, who sent me, you ask? It was <Friend Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "Hm. So I had more power hidden inside me.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Guess I've improved a bit.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I still have a ways to go.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Thanks. I'll pay you back on the battlefield.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "Since meeting you all, I've learned that strength comes in many forms. The strength to protect peace... is not the strength I learned as a gladiator, killing for sport. I've learned much from you, <Player Name>. And I will learn more yet. I will become stronger. I will learn to swing my blade in service of a lasting peace.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
